data.description: Turn Key Ready home awaits you! This home has been well taken care of by sellers and ready for new owners to enjoy.  3 bedrooms and 3 FULL bathrooms.  Master bedroom is oversized with an enormous walking closet! Carpet was recently replaced, all new interior paint, and new blinds to all windows. Tile on the bottom floor and beautiful floor laminate on family room.  Water Osmosis through out the whole house.  Enjoy your beautiful kitchen with all stainless steel appliances! Laundry room is located upstairs, making it convenience.  Patio is all pavers and ready for a gathering or bbq. Bottom room can be utilized for office space or for guests with full bathroom access without having to go upstairs. Your eyes will be pleased upon entering. Enjoy!
